* Exception Handling
 EXCEPTION
 TRY
 RAISE          alternate 1
* Parameter Control
 DEFAULT        alternate 4
 IN             alternate 4
 INOUT          alternate 4
 OUT            alternate 4
 WITH           alternate 4
* Binary Operations
 AND            alternate 1
 NOT            alternate 1
 OR             alternate 1
* Data Types and Storage containers
 Array          alternate 6
 Boolean        alternate 2
 Bytes          alternate 2
